premise_source_doc_sentence: Keanu Charles Reeves  (  -LSB- kiːˈɑːnuː -RSB- ; born September 2 , 1964  )  is a Canadian actor , director , producer , and musician .
Keanu primarily refers to Keanu Reeves  (  born 1964  )  , a Canadian actor and director .

Bill & Ted is a series of two films  (  and their spin-offs  )  featuring William `` Bill '' S. Preston Esq.  (  Alex Winter  )  and `` Ted '' Theodore Logan  (  Keanu Reeves  )  as two metalhead slackers who travel through time .
